<p class="ql-align-center">火锅粉、牛肉炒凉粉、包子、炸锁骨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花甲粉等超多你意想不到的美味！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为一个侯志伟女孩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天就带大家一起打卡侯志伟美食！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>侯志伟酸辣粉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200913/a1d837074376433da06644bf80a5a505.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">侯志伟手工酸辣粉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">光是看到名字就已经开始让人口水四溢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他家无论走哪儿都是人人人人人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">排队一堆人，嗦粉一堆人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200913/70445986fa104ee5925d7e8fe3481469.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">绝对是吃一口就上瘾的香辣和酸爽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他家粉是纯手工红薯粉，粉比较粗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">配上各式调味品和最诱人的肉酱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">粉和汤料相辅相成，但却都是主角</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200913/810fb7b75c7d4fbda7c2699e8105e1fc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">粉比一般的酸辣粉要稍微粗一点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">细腻光滑，韧而不老，酸辣爽滑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">汤底红油油一片，辣而不燥 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200913/4881d812c7824318b029fa32f05434ec.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一碗酸辣粉吃起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">酸香、麻辣、爽口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每一口味道融合的都恰到好处</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200913/4c5bbfd39d4a4ba6a792fc0e274364bd.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>侯志伟老街螺蛳粉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">专业做酸辣粉的侯志伟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">居然也进攻了螺蛳粉界</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在西安螺蛳粉界纵横多年的爱吃君</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无论韦姐黄姐还是蒋姐就没有没吃过的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200913/3789b338584d47bf97aae933d45d4d82.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（黄姐螺蛳粉）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以，一开始对这个螺蛳粉界“新秀”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并没有太多的期待</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但尝过后，虽不至于啪啪打脸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但是也稍微有被它的口味惊喜到 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200913/780e801bdd5b47e19256190a4442b3de.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一份原汤的螺蛳粉是13元</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱吃君点上了份16元的套餐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">加上了几个菜还有一瓶冰峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">价格还是比较划算的，分量也足 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200913/3f67cf977fa34f3fa98369d50a24890d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200913/133b0b4d133848c1a09c261378fbd321.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这碗螺蛳粉整体来说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">口味还是很不错的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有柳州螺蛳粉内味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">配菜虽然不算出色，但也入味好吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但是，它的粉吃起来口感很一般</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有些糯糯的，不好咬断</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有那种Q弹爽滑的韧性嚼劲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给整体稍稍有点扣分</p>
